OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright
OL,6,Fspells and a few showers during the
OL,7,Fevening. A band of cloud and outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain will then move south
OL,9,Fovernight, with northern Highland and
OL,10,Fthe Isles turning clearer again
OL,11,Ftowards morning.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FCloud and patchy rain will
OL,14,Fclear from the south early morning.
OL,15,FOtherwise a bright day with sunny
OL,16,Fspells and scattered showers, these
OL,17,Fwintry on the mountains. Feeling cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
